      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/{size}/1331_2.png",
      "created_at": "2020-11-30T12:31:04.309Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I actually want to get rid of the bottom menu but still allow hot swap.  Ride with GPS does this nicely.</p>\n<p>They just show a popup, but it still keeps going even if you close it.  This give syou extra space but allows this hotswap.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/1X/d4cb79463a02c8692d027e4fca0304634d29d435.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/d4cb79463a02c8692d027e4fca0304634d29d435\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/d4cb79463a02c8692d027e4fca0304634d29d435_2_567x500.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"umtab8ffil8ngo762Farm9ot07b\" width=\"567\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/d4cb79463a02c8692d027e4fca0304634d29d435_2_567x500.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/d4cb79463a02c8692d027e4fca0304634d29d435_2_850x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/1X/d4cb79463a02c8692d027e4fca0304634d29d435.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/d4cb79463a02c8692d027e4fca0304634d29d435_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">979\u00d7862 124 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
