      "created_at": "2020-11-30T12:38:20.195Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I guess I was just thinking of ways I would change the GUI for my use case\u2026 interesting to hear of how other people use the app. I do think either making the current vs target power bigger or making it possible to re-arrange the screen would help me a lot.</p>",
