      "created_at": "2020-11-30T12:39:13.845Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Yes I agree on zoom feature.  For now I think the simple solution is making the chart tappable for 3-different zoom levels.  5m, 20m and full workout.  As far as font sizes go, I think ours right now are as large or larger than almost everyones on a phone.  That said my eyes are similar to your and I would be happier with even bigger.</p>",
