      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/{size}/1331_2.png",
      "created_at": "2020-11-30T12:41:55.635Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Yes that is expensive option (user arrangable screens), and I am avoiding expensive solutions but also trying to make it the best possible for as many people as possible and bigger fonts are always welcome.  I also want it as clear as possible for the beginner and advanced person so I prefer to state Target to make it extra clear.  The zoom feature is the one I can see coming the soonest <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"> Tablet is obviously way to see bigger fonts. If I can switch from bottom tabs to popup that gives us more room for bigger for sure.  But that won\u2019t be right away\u2026</p>",
