      "created_at": "2020-11-30T12:54:45.338Z",
      "cooked": "<p>When I\u2019m using the workouts of my plan, I don\u2019t need the hot-swap feature. But when I just hop on the bike on the days with no planned workout, I really love this hot-swapping. But maybe it can be done without using so much real-estate on the screen.<br>\nAnd I\u2019m using the app on an 11-inch-iPad where you don\u2019t have the same problems regarding space.</p>",
